Prepare a dataframe with URLs for cat pics.

Source: R/kittypics_df_maker.R
kitty_pics_df.Rd

Prepare a dataframe with URLs for cat pics.

kitty_pics_df(url, ...)

Arguments

url

URL for the source from which individual image URLs are to be extracted.
...

Currently ignored.

Examples

kittyR::kitty_pics_df("https://unsplash.com/s/photos/kitten/")
